title: My Insanely Competent Underlings
alternative_titles: 我的疯批部下超级有能力
summary: The depths of the labyrinth that leads to hell where it’s impossible to retreat. Gamers, who entered the ranks of heroes, and even those who were called the absolute powers of a generation failed to clear the deep zone. “Unless a miracle happens, all of you will die. Are you ready to die?” My team members replied with stern faces. “No.” “No.” “No.”…No one?! Hoyeon’s rise to the top with his insanely competent—or just crazy—teammates in a game fantasy. My Insanely Strong Henchmen, My Insanely Competent Underlings, 我的疯批部下超级有能力, 내 부하들이 미친듯이 유능하다
